## Naming Conventions

- **Components**: PascalCase (`LogoLink`, `NavMenuProvider`)
- **Files**: Match component/export name (`LogoLink.tsx`, `helpers.ts`)
- **Variables & Functions**: camelCase (`isOpen`, `scrollToTop`)
- **Constants**: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE (`DEFAULT_LOCALE`, `NAV_MENU_OPENING_DURATION`)
- **Types/Interfaces**: PascalCase (`LogoLinkProps`, `NavMenuContextType`)
- **Hooks**: camelCase starting with `use` (`useNavMenu`, `useLocale`)

